SUMMARY:Monday Morning Yoga - HYBRID in-person / virtual
DESCRIPTION:Early Spring Session: April 6\, 13\, 20\, 27 \nMondays\, 9:30 AM – 10:45 AM \nInstructor: Jennifer Hondru-Celestin \nJoin our welcoming community for a meditative yoga flow practice in the Van Vleck living room overlooking the charming courtyard gardens. All levels of yoga experience are welcome in this dynamic\, inclusive class. Our teacher Jennifer Hondru-Celestin takes inspiration from the natural beauty around us to flow with the seasons\, blending mindful movement\, breath\, meditation\, and a good dose of humor and fun.  This class welcomes all levels from beginner to experienced yogis. Bring your own yoga mat and props. \nFee:  Single class: $23 Members / $28 Non-Members \nSeries (9 classes): $180 members and $225 general public
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/monday-morning-yoga-hybrid-in-person-virtual-12-8/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults,Virtual
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2026/01/Monday-Yoga--e1768594760941.jpg
END:VEVENT
